                     <interp inst="t18391125-190-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18391125-cd-173" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18391125-190-offence-1 t18391125-cd-173"></join>19th of No<lb></lb>vember</rs>, 3 pewter pots, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18391125-name-955" type="victimName">
